            .</p>
               <p>* 
               <persName id="t17861025-100-person1244">
                  Charles
                   Hale
               <interp inst="t17861025-100-person1244" type="surname" value="Hale"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17861025-100-person1244" type="given" value="Charles"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17861025-100-person1244" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             served on the London Jury, the 7th day, in the room of 
               <persName id="t17861025-100-person1245">
                  Joseph
                   Wells
               <interp inst="t17861025-100-person1245" type="surname" value="Wells"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17861025-100-person1245" type="given" value="Joseph"></interp>
